extendedInfo.description: OWASP AppSec Research is the European conference for anyone interested in application security. This year it will be hosted by the Department of Informatics and Telecommunications of the University of Athens, Greece and will take place between July 10-13th. OWASP AppSec Research 2012 conference is practically the OWASP AppSec Europe.
